- url = signmein_url(u: @user.uid, t: @user.login_token)

%p
  Hello
  = @user.formal_name + ','

%p
  Here is your login link. Please click on the link below to sign in automatically to the Control Room of the Lord Mayor's Show:

%h3
  = link_to ">> Sign in here", url

%p
  If you prefer you can cut and paste the same address into your browser:

%code
  %pre
    = url

%p
  This link expires at 
  = l(@user.login_token_created_at + Droom.config.login_token_ttl, format: :natural_on_date) + '.'
  If you did not request the link, you can safely ignore or delete this message.
